title: Beautiful Renovated 2 BD 2 BA Apartment - Available Now!
posting_body: ['Newly renovated 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom (Fully renovated bathrooms) apartment with lots of natural light.', 'This unit has a Large Living Room with fire place, Kitchen, and Dining area next to each other.', 'Hardwood floors, lots of closet space, and private access to a shared deck.', 'Perfect home for someone who loves being in a lively area.', 'Conveniently located in the Mission district, just a couple of blocks away from Dolores Park.', 'KEY FEATURES', '• Square Footage: 1000 sq.', 'ft', '• Two Bedroom (one of the rooms is a master suite)', '• Two Bath', '• Lease Duration: 12 Month lease', '• Pets Policy: No Pets Allowed', '• Property Type: Apartment', '• Laundry on site', 'RENTAL FEATURES', '• Large Living room/ Dining/ Kitchen/ Upgraded Bathrooms', '• Gas Range/Oven', '• Refrigerator', '* Dishwasher', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES.', '3505 19th Street is conveniently located in the sunny Mission District right in the corner of Valencia and 19th St. Public transportation is close by.', 'Tons of local shops and a variety of restaurants to choose from.', 'Walking distance to Dolores Park.', 'Rockwell Properties Management', '109 Bartlett St Suite 201 San Francisco, CA', 'BRE 00872023', 'OFFICE HOURS: Monday to Friday 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM', 'CONTACT US TODAY at Tel.', '#', 'show contact info']
